channel.title: Seeing More Content From Someone?
channel.description:
Well, personally, I'd like to see more tutorials from Blakeman, more server releases from Graham, and more server development from Canownueasy. I'd really love to have more tutorials from Blakeman though.
And I want the equipping items method Canownueasy has in FlareSoft and convert it to a PI base, and the clipped following he has in there as well. Those are my top 2 things I want the most.

item.title: Seeing More Content From Someone?
item.dc:creator: @Rixxx Rix_
item.description:
@Rixxx wrote:

We’re dead.

MoparScape is basically a place where people join to ask a question and leave, regardless of getting an answer, after a week. Most of the tutorials we see here are by R-S people who just contribute for the sake of it, otherwise it’s from us and most of them are snippets/common sense. Server releases and projects here are rarely frameworks; people keep using those horrible bases.

The majority of people with 200 rep no longer do anything, we’re just here for discussions.

Edit: Well I guess you can also say we’re not progressing and haven’t been for 9999999.

Read full topic
